<headline>Lake Wind Advisory issued April 03 at 3:54AM PDT until April 04 at 8:00PM PDT by NWS Reno</headline>
<description>...LAKE WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 11 AM TO 8 PM PDT MONDAY FOR
PYRAMID LAKE...
* WHAT...West winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 45 mph
expected. Waves 3 to 5 feet.
* WHERE...Pyramid Lake.
* WHEN...From 11 AM to 8 PM PDT Monday.
* IMPACTS...Small boats, kayaks and paddle boards will be prone to
capsizing and should remain off lake waters until conditions
improve.</description>
<instruction>Check lake conditions before heading out and be prepared for a
sudden increase in winds and wave heights. Consider postponing
boating activities on the lake until a day with less wind.</instruction>
